Package de.hsrt.holbox.Models

Class ElectricalActor

java.lang.Object
de.hsrt.holbox.Models.ElectricalActor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConventionalGenerator, Photovoltaic, Storage
public abstract class ElectricalActor extends Object
Parent class for all Actors in the electrical power system this includes: Generators, Loads, FACTS, etc. but does not include other passive equipment such as lines, transformers, busbars, protections. These would under the category Electrical Actor.
Author:
notholt
